iptables -A FORWARD -m state --state RELATED,ESTABLISHED -j ACCEPT

1) Domain name resolutions using the dns server

Máquina2(DMZ, dns) <-> qualquer endereço

iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.2 -p tcp --dport domain -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.2 -p tcp --sport domain -j ACCEPT

Máquina1(Rede Pública):
ip addr add 172.16.1.1/24 dev enp0s8
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 172.16.1.254
nc 50.40.30.2 53

Máquina2(DMZ, dns):
ip addr add 50.40.30.2/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 172.16.1.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc -l 53


2) The dns server should be able to resolve names using DNS servers on the Internet

Máquina2(DMZ, dns) <-> Máquina1(Rede Pública)

Regras router:
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.2 -d 172.16.1.0/24 -p tcp --dport domain -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.2 -s 172.16.1.0/24 -p tcp --sport domain -j ACCEPT

Máquina1(Rede Pública):
ip addr add 172.16.1.1/24 dev enp0s8
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 172.16.1.254
nc -l 53

Máquina2(DMZ, dns):
ip addr add 50.40.30.2/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 172.16.1.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc 172.16.1.1 53


3) The dns and dns2 servers should be able to synchronize the contents of DNS zones

Máquina2(DMZ, dns) <-> Máquina1(Rede Pública, dns2)

Regras router:
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.2 -d 172.16.1.3 -p tcp --dport domain -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.2 -s 172.16.1.3 -p tcp --sport domain -j ACCEPT

Máquina1(Rede Pública, dns2):
ip addr add 172.16.1.3/24 dev enp0s8
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 172.16.1.254
nc -l 53

Máquina2(DMZ, dns):
ip addr add 50.40.30.2/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 172.16.1.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc 172.16.1.3 53


4) SMTP connections to the smtp server

Máquina2(DMZ, smtp) <-> qualquer endereço

Regras router:
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.3 -p tcp --dport smtp -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.3 -p tcp --sport smtp -j ACCEPT

Máquina1(Rede Pública):
ip addr add 172.16.1.1/24 dev enp0s8
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 172.16.1.254
nc 50.40.30.3 25

Máquina2(DMZ, smtp):
ip addr add 50.40.30.3/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 172.16.1.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc -l 25


5) POP and IMAP connections to the mail server

Máquina2(DMZ, mail) <-> qualquer endereço

Regras router:
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.4 -p tcp --dport pop3 -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.4 -p tcp --sport pop3 -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.4 -p tcp --dport imap -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.4 -p tcp --sport imap -j ACCEPT

Máquina1(Rede Pública):
ip addr add 172.16.1.1/24 dev enp0s8
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 172.16.1.254
nc 50.40.30.4 110 (pop)
nc 50.40.30.4 143 (imap)

Máquina2(DMZ, mail):
ip addr add 50.40.30.4/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 172.16.1.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc -l 110 (pop)
nc -l 143 (imap)


6) HTTP and HTTPS connections to the www server

Máquina2(DMZ, www) <-> qualquer endereço

Regras router:
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.5 -p tcp --dport http -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.5 -p tcp --sport http -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.5 -p tcp --dport https -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.5 -p tcp --sport https -j ACCEPT

Máquina1(Rede Pública):
ip addr add 172.16.1.1/24 dev enp0s8
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 172.16.1.254
nc 50.40.30.5 80 (http)
nc 50.40.30.5 443 (https)

Máquina2(DMZ, www):
ip addr add 50.40.30.5/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 172.16.1.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc -l 80 (http)
nc -l 443 (https)


7) OpenVPN connections to the vpn-gw server

Máquina2(DMZ, vpn-gw) <-> qualquer endereço

Regras router:
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.1 -p tcp --dport openvpn -j ACCEPT
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.1 -p tcp --sport openvpn -j ACCEPT

Máquina1(Rede Pública):
ip addr add 172.16.1.1/24 dev enp0s8
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 172.16.1.254
nc 50.40.30.1 1194 (vpn)

Máquina2(DMZ, vpn-gw):
ip addr add 50.40.30.1/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 172.16.1.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc -l 1194 (vpn)


8) VPN clients connected to the gateway (vpn-gw) should be able to connect to all services in the Internal network

Regras router:
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.1 -d 10.254.0.2 -p tcp --dport domain -j ACCEPT 
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.1 -s 10.254.0.2 -p tcp --sport domain -j ACCEPT 
iptables -A FORWARD -s 50.40.30.1 -d 10.254.0.3 -p tcp --dport domain -j ACCEPT 
iptables -A FORWARD -d 50.40.30.1 -s 10.254.0.3 -p tcp --sport domain -j ACCEPT 

Máquina1(DMZ, vpn-gw):
ip addr add 50.40.30.1/24 dev enp0s9
route add -net 10.254.0.0/24 gw 50.40.30.254
nc 10.254.0.2 53 (datastore)
nc 10.254.0.3 53 (ftp)

Máquina2(Rede privada):
ip addr add 10.254.0.2/24 dev enp0s8 (datastore)
ip addr add 10.254.0.3/24 dev enp0s8 (ftp)
route add -net 50.40.30.0/24 gw 10.254.0.254
nc -l 53 (datastore)
nc -l 53 (ftp)
